            . I live in Artichoke-court, Cannon-street. The prisoner and another person named Ladd used to sleep on the ruins by the new bridge; I used to take them bread and food: on the 2nd of August I was sent with a bundle - I told Hall and 
               <persName id="t18311020-39-person344">Ladd</persName>
             I was going with it; as I went along Ladd snatched the bundle from me - the prisoner was with him; the parcel belonged to my uncle, 
